These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, water
4 different games are played: go, scrabble, poker, bridge
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
3. the person playing poker is between the person playing scrabble and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Game      | bridge | go | poker   | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
4 different pets are kept: horse, dog, chinchilla, frog
1. the owner of the frog is between the person who's hobby is reading and the owner of the dog##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Pet   | dog    | frog   | horse | chinchilla       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, scientific, zombie
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, british, colombian, french
1. the colombian is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the colombian is between the british and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the british is on the far left##1
4. the french is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | zombie    | epic | martial-arts   | scientific  |
| Nationality   | british | colombian   | french | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony, rat
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, brown, pink, fuchsia
1. the person who likes brown is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the person who likes lavender and the owner of the rat##2
3. the person who likes brown is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Pet     | rat   | cat    | pony       | lizard   |
| Color   | pink | fuchsia | lavender | brown |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, soy-milk
There are 4 different nationalities: german, spanish, british, japanese
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the british is on the far left##1
3. the german is on the far right##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is between the german and the spanish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Beverage   | fanta        | iced-tea | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality      | british | spanish  | japanese | german    |

