.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, pop, salsa
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, strawberry, orange, cherry
1. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
2. the fan of salsa is the person eating orange##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is the person eating artichoke##1
5. the fan of pop is between the fan of classical and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | pop           | classical | salsa  |
| Food         | artichoke | cherry | strawberry   | orange |

