.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, december, march, november
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person who's birthday is in december is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person driving the bus and the person who's birthday is in march##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday   | november   | december | june | march      |
| Transport     | roller | bus    | motorbike  | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, soccer, weightlifting
House: victorian, colonial, wooden, cape-cod
1. the victorian house is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the colonial house is between the person who's sport is soccer and the wooden house##2
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
4. the victorian house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | biathlon | weightlifting | soccer     | lacrosse   |
| House   | wooden   | colonial     | cape-cod | victorian |

