.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, entrepreneur, librarian, videographer
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, lemonade, cola, fanta
1. the librarian is between the person drinking milk and the dressmaker##2
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the dressmaker##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | entrepreneur | librarian | dressmaker | videographer |
| Beverage   | milk         | fanta       | lemonade    | cola         |

