.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, water-polo, handball, baseball
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, superhero, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Sport          | skateboarding     | water-polo | baseball   | handball        |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | superhero   | fantasy | time-travel |

