.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, musical, zombie, drama
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, pop, punk, trance
1. the fan of punk is the person watching musical movies##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of gospel is the person watching western movies##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is the fan of pop##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
6. the fan of pop is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching drama movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre         | musical | zombie | drama | western |
| Music-Genre   | punk          | pop     | trance  | gospel     |

