2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
3. the librarian is on the right of the doctor##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the librarian##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Job           | doctor | librarian | firefighter | entrepreneur |
| Hobby   | skydiving   | filmmaking | dancing         | chess |

