1. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the spanish is the person who's sport is cricket##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is badminton and the italian##2
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | italian | egyptian | pakistani |
| Sport           | cricket  | water-polo  | golf | badminton      |

