.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, puzzles, rock-climbing, singing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bongani, siglo, fonseca
1. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
2. the game-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the game-smoker and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the game-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby       | singing | puzzles | rock-climbing | collecting |
| Cigar   | game    | bongani  | fonseca    | siglo       |

