.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese, polish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, spy, thriller, crime
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the polish is the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person watching crime movies is between the american and the chinese##2
5. the chinese is the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish   | american   | australian | chinese |
| Movie-Genre         | time-travel | spy | crime     | thriller    |

