.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, american, british, colombian
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1
2. the mexican is between the owner of the cat and the colombian##2
3. the colombian is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the american is on the far right##1
5. the american is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | british    | colombian     | mexican | american |
| Pet     | chinchilla | guinea-pig | goat       | cat     |

 